sentences: Robin Albers (born 1956), who uses the stage name Jaydee, is a Dutch house music producer and DJ.
His original stage name was Jei D. In 1992, under the stage name JayDee, he released "Plastic Dreams", which reached number-one on the US Billboard Hot Dance Music/Club Play chart.
The track made the UK Singles Chart on two occasions; firstly in September 1997 when it reached number 18, and again in January 2004, when it reached number 35.
